promed@promedmail.org


[Classical swine fever has officially been reported to the OIE, since the
beginning of 2002, from the following countries(in brackets - date of
latest report): Bulgaria (26 Apr 2002); France (10 May 2002); Germany (03
May 2002); S.Korea (03 May 2002); Luxembourg (05 Apr 2002); Romania (12 Apr
2002); Slovenia (15 Mar 2002). See
<http://www.oie.int/eng/info/hebdo/a_dsum.htm>.- Mod. AS]
